  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators intend to study the role of the cortex in high- level cognition processes
      and sensory adaptation, by the use of non-invasive Transcranial Magnetic stimulation and
      various cognitive tests.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
